  <brief_title>Rituximab in Combination With Fludarabine and Cyclophosphamide in Patients With Chronic Lymphocytic Leukemia</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open, Non-Interventional, Multicentre Trial of Rituximab in Combination With FC for the First-Line Therapy of Patients With Chronic Lymphocytic Leukaemia</official_title>
