  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Evaluation of safety profile and tolerability of MabThera (rituximab) in combination with
      chemotherapy (fludarabine and cyclophosphamide) in the treatment of Chronic Lymphocytic
      Leukemia (CLL).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
